        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You're wielding an unloaded firearm.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You jam a triple charge of black powder into your weapon to unleash a devastating but risky and inaccurate attack. Interact to reload, expending three doses of black powder in addition to your normal black powder or ammunition, then Strike with your firearm against a creature within the weapon's first range increment. If you roll a success, the attack is instead a critical success, but if you roll a failure, the weapon misfires. Regardless of your roll, after the attack you're @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] until the start of your next turn and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 1}.</p>"
